snippet.title: Best VGM 2405 - Paper Mario - Goomba Village
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1253 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BimaIgvOa-A



A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Paper Mario (2000)
Goomba Village
Yuka Tsujiyoko & Taishi Senda
